<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN206-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. atiyamāṉ neṭumāṉañci pariciṉīṭṭittāṉai auvaiyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div> 
    <div xml:id="PN206">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vāyi lōyē vāyi lōyē</l>
<l>vaḷḷiyōr cevimutal vayaṅkumoḻi vittit</l>
<l>tām, muṉṉiyatu muṭikku muraṉuṭai yuḷḷattu</l>
<l>varicaikku varuntumip paricil vāḻkkaip</l>
<l>paricilark kaṭaiyā vāyi lōyē</l>
<l>kaṭumāṉ ṟōṉṟa ṉeṭumā ṉañci</l>
<l>taṉṉaṟi yalaṉko leṉṉaṟi yalaṉko</l>
<l>laṟivum pukaḻu muṭaiyōr māynteṉa</l>
<l>vaṟuntalai yulakamu maṉṟē yataṉāṟ</l>
<l>kāviṉeṅ kalaṉē curukkiṉeṅ kalappai</l>
<l>maraṅko ṟaccaṉ kaival ciṟāar</l>
<l>maḻuvuṭaik kāṭṭakat taṟṟē</l>
<l>yetticaic celiṉu matticaic cōṟē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">Doorman! Doorman! </l>
<l corresp="2">Sowing glowing words into the ears of generous people </l>
<l corresp="3">with strong minds that achieve what they considered, </l>
<l corresp="4">with this living for gifts that suffers for marks of honour, </l>
<l corresp="5">doormen who do not close against/exclude gift-seekers: </l>
<l corresp="6">Neṭumaṉ Añci who appears on a fast horse, </l>
<l corresp="7">does he not know himself? Does he not know me? </l>
<l corresp="8">Because those who have both knowledge and fame vanish </l>
<l corresp="9">the world is not a poor place. Therefore, </l>
<l corresp="10">We shoulder the vessels. We fold up the instrument bags. </l>
<l corresp="12">It is like the inside of a forest with axes [in the hands] </l>
<l corresp="11">of the dexterous youngsters of the carpenter who fells trees: </l>
<l corresp="13"> In whatever direction [we] go, in that direction there is rice. </l>   
</lg>
    </div>
